{"word":"Isaac","slug":"isaac","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Isaac</b> - (Laughter) son of Abraham and Sarah<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=19'>Gen 17:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=3'>Gen 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=12'>Gen 21:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=2'>Gen 22:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=4'>Gen 24:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=12'>Gen 26:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=1'>Gen 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=29'>Gen 35:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=31'>Gen 49:31</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=17'>Heb 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=20'>Heb 11:20</a><p/>Characteristics of<p/>--Submission<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=6'>Ge 22:6-9</a><p/>--Meditation<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=63'>Ge 24:63</a><p/>--Affection<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=67'>Ge 24:67</a><p/>--Imitated his father's sin<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=7'>Ge 26:7</a><p/>--Peaceableness<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=20'>Ge 26:20-22</a><p/>--Prayerfulness<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=25'>Ge 26:25</a><p/>--A man of faith<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=20'>Heb 11:20</a>"}]}